summary: Report on a meeting with AMWHIP-1 regarding the possibility of placing AMBUNNY in UNSNAFU-19's mission in Paris as a French-English-Spanish speaking secretary. The meeting covered AMBUNNY's qualifications and the potential difficulties in concealing her background. The author also reflects on AMWHIP-1's personality and approach to problem-solving.
title: Contact Report, Meeting with AMWHIP-1
